headline: EV Pickups Are a Bust for US Carmakers

headline: CARHAUL TEAMSTERS HOLD AREA STANDARDS PICKET
summary: Carhaul Teamsters from Locals 89, 332, and 604 have launched area standards pickets outside General Motors Plants in Michigan, Kentucky, and Missouri. The actions targeted nonunion carriers operating out of GM's Flint, Bowling Green, and Wentzville Assembly plants.
